dmca.title: Google Requested to Take Down Yahoo! Chat Posted on Internet
dmca.body:
[private]@optonline.net

Warwick, NY  10990

March 26, 2004

Google Inc.
Attn: User Support, DMCA Complaints
[Private]
Mountain View, CA  94043

Google, Inc.:

Please remove from the Google site all links to private conversations of mine from closed yahoo chat groups.

1.) The copyrighted work at issue appears on www.google.com/search?hl=en&ie=UTF8+oe= UTF8+q=Yvonne+Muller&btng=google+search

2.) Search query: [private]
Infringing web pages: members4.boardhost.com/egphototips/msg/607.html
